This paper deals with deep generative models for handling multi-aspect data with missing observations, which is a common problem in machine learning and related application areas. The paper also focuses on disentangling the groups and the latent dimensions, which is a key issue in many of these problems. Therefore, the most likely arXiv CS sub-categories for this paper are cs.LG (Machine Learning), cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), cs.CV (Computer Vision), cs.CL (Computation and Language), and cs.SD (Sound).
